screen_desc: The screenshot displays a user profile interface from a messaging app. The profile belongs to a user named "Tri," who is currently online. It features a profile picture of a cat and includes the user's phone number, username, and a section for a bio. There are options to edit the profile information, set a profile photo, change the profile color, and log out. Below the profile section, there are various settings options, including chat settings, privacy and security, notifications and sounds, data and storage, power saving, chat folders, and devices. The interface has a blue background with white text.
